title: War of the Roses: A Timestamp is Worth a Thousand Words
description: On this BRAND NEW War of the Roses, Ashley's boyfriend is supposed to be quarantined with his mom but when she asked him to send a picture of the two of them, the timestamp on it said it was from months ago.  Now she's wondering if he's really been with his mom this whole time...
